OL,3,CLong delays on M1 in Leicestershire
OL,4,Cafter a two vehicle crash
OL,6,FA section of the M1 in Leicestershire
OL,7,Fhave been closed following a two
OL,8,Fvehicle crash.
OL,10,FAt around 2pm on Friday, National
OL,11,FHighways confirmed that the motorway
OL,12,Fwas closed in both directions between
OL,13,FJ21 Leicester and J20 Lutterworth.
OL,15,FThe closure lead to long delays in
OL,16,Fwhat would be the Friday afternoon
OL,17,Frush.
OL,19,FLeicestershire Police and Fire and
OL,20,FRescue Service said they had crews
OL,21,Fattending the scene.
