OL,3,CLong delays on M1 in Leicestershire
OL,4,Cafter a two vehicle crash
OL,6,FThey advised motorists should avoid
OL,7,Fthe area and expect delays.
OL,9,FNational Highways said an accident
OL,10,Finvestigation would have to be carried
OL,11,Fout before the road can reopen.
